options.text: Yes, I would like to charter a ship.

89b70ec9-d2a3-4b9e-bdbd-7923a9a3abc5.title: Trader Crewmember
89b70ec9-d2a3-4b9e-bdbd-7923a9a3abc5.text:
I'm one of Trader Stan's crew; we are all part of the
largest fleet of trading and sailing vessels to ever sail
the seven seas.

8301adf1-2e3f-4777-b7fd-4da9abb031f5.title: Trader Crewmember
8301adf1-2e3f-4777-b7fd-4da9abb031f5.text:
If you want to get to a port in a hurry then you can
charter one of our ships to take you there - if the price
is right...

7bf559d0-5ccd-4794-9106-6b837b2997d7.title: <player>
7bf559d0-5ccd-4794-9106-6b837b2997d7.text: So, where exactly can I go with your ships?

7b34ba1c-55b5-47ec-a884-a1dd2752ad0d.title: Trader Crewmember
7b34ba1c-55b5-47ec-a884-a1dd2752ad0d.text:
We run ships from Port Phasmatys over to Port
Tyras, stopping at Port Sarim, Catherby, Brimhaven,
Musa Point, the Shipyard and Port Khazard.

2b20a113-e2f5-4b04-aa1d-3f0b357603de.title: Trader Crewmember
2b20a113-e2f5-4b04-aa1d-3f0b357603de.text:
We might dock at Mos Le'Harmless once in a while, as
well, if you catch my meaning...

83a5a913-e5d3-4e52-8dcd-489fdb441941.title: <player>
83a5a913-e5d3-4e52-8dcd-489fdb441941.text:
Wow, that's a lot of ports. I take it you have some
exotic stuff to trade?

17aafd3f-3425-4bf5-93e6-8fa4ec889f51.title: Trader Crewmember
17aafd3f-3425-4bf5-93e6-8fa4ec889f51.text:
We certainly do! We have access to items bought and
sold from around the world. Would you like to take a
look? Or would you like to charter a ship?

options.text: Yes, let's see what you're trading.
Yes, I would like to charter a ship.
Isn't it tricky to sail about in those clothes?

f0c88e08-c471-41cb-abbb-477db16ac09a.title: <player>
f0c88e08-c471-41cb-abbb-477db16ac09a.text: Yes, let's see what you're trading.

b82ca91c-9bb5-4a69-93c4-856bc0cc1418.title: <player>
b82ca91c-9bb5-4a69-93c4-856bc0cc1418.text: Isn't it tricky to sail about in those clothes?

03fb832f-dc3f-4660-a169-5c593db8777d.title: Trader Crewmember
03fb832f-dc3f-4660-a169-5c593db8777d.text:
With all due credit, Trader Stan is a great employer,
but he insists we wear the latest in high fashion even
when sailing.

83157322-165a-4fe0-a0e3-4b8ef7e79870.title: Trader Crewmember
83157322-165a-4fe0-a0e3-4b8ef7e79870.text:
Do you have even the slightest idea how tricky it is to
sail in this stuff?

12e665f9-babc-4e22-a98f-8bd7e9abee85.title: Trader Crewmember
12e665f9-babc-4e22-a98f-8bd7e9abee85.text:
Some of us tried tearing it and arguing that it was too
fragile to wear when on a boat, but he just had it
enchanted to re-stitch itself.

45485ab8-287b-402c-b0a3-74ed62042f38.title: Trader Crewmember
45485ab8-287b-402c-b0a3-74ed62042f38.text:
It's hard to hate him when we know how much he shells
out on this gear, but if I fall overboard because of this
getup one more time, I'm going to quit.

1ec95e0c-7b12-454c-bab7-2e463e3753b1.title: Trader Crewmember
1ec95e0c-7b12-454c-bab7-2e463e3753b1.text:
Anyway, would you like to take a look at our exotic
wares from around the world? Or would you like to
charter a ship?

options.text: Yes, let's see what you're trading.
Yes, I would like to charter a ship.
